DAVID HANSCOM: OK.

00:45:32.975 --> 00:45:35.391
SACHIT EGAN: And the question
is, "Does your approach work

00:45:35.391 --> 00:45:36.530
for all kinds of back pain?

00:45:36.530 --> 00:45:38.000
And if not, can
